For example the distribution of intelligence in society, but you could also take the size of men, the number of households with kitchen mixer ... but you would have to find out whether it is really normal distribution, even paranormal distribution or just random or conicidence
To compensate low self-esteem (object fixation) with this once-received laurel wreath. About as Intelligent as using always the one and same One-Time-Pad

A laurel wreath is a wreath made of branches and leaves of the laurel (latin laurus). The laurel wreath is a symbol and an insignia for a special honor or distinction, for a victory (eg. killing sheeps or christians) or a special success. So to say the special super-duper superman hero
Agreeableness: Not at all, too imperative
